reviewText: I really enjoyed watching this. I am a big Elton John fan but I didn't really pay attention to his life much and this documentary helped me understand the man a lot more.

I had to write this on Sir Elton's 67th birthday!  A program that originally aired in 2007 on the Biography Network, this covers Sir Elton John from his humble beginnings through the beginning of the Las Vegas Red Piano shows.

I highly recommend this item for any EJ fan...young or old!!
I've loved Elton since 1973 and collecting everything he has put out from albums to CD and all else in between.  Had this on VHS and upgraded to the DVD. It's great and so is he!
